#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:3
msgid ""
"A section is the lowest unit on the Course hierarchy and it consists in a "
"single webpage.\n"
"Every section has its own title and content."
msgstr ""

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:3
msgid "Add a section"
msgstr "Einen Abschnitt hinzufügen"

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:7
msgid ""
"To add a section into a chapter, go the course main page. \n"
"Find the chapter where you want to add the section and click on the pencil "
"on the right of the chapter's name. \n"
"Write the name of the section and save the changes by clicking on the <code>"
"save chapter</code> button."
msgstr ""

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:7
msgid "Rename a section"
msgstr "Einen Abschnitt umbenennen"

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:12
msgid ""
"Simply find the chapter where the section is located and click on the pencil "
"on the right of the chapter's name. \n"
"You will be able to rename the section by clicking on the icon with the blue "
"pencil."
msgstr ""

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:15
msgid "[[File:Manual_rename_section.gif]]"
msgstr "[[File:Manual_rename_section.gif]]"

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:15
msgid "Delete a section"
msgstr "Einen Abschnitt löschen"

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:18
msgid ""
"To delete a section find the chapter where the targeted section is present "
"and edit it.\n"
"You will be able to delete the section by pressing on the trash icon."
msgstr ""

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:21
msgid "[[File:Manual_delete_section.gif]]"
msgstr "[[File:Manual_delete_section.gif]]"

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:21
msgid "Restore a section"
msgstr "Einen Abschnitt wiederherstellen"

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:24
msgid ""
"If you have sections in the recycling bin you can restore them by placing "
"the mouse on the sections and clicking on the restore icon on the left of "
"the section's name."
msgstr ""

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:26
msgid "[[File:Manual_Restore_section.gif]]"
msgstr "[[File:Manual_Restore_section.gif]]"

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:28
msgid ""
"Always remember to save the changes by clicking on the <code>Save "
"Course</code> button."
msgstr ""

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:28
msgid "Move a section"
msgstr "Einen Abschnitt verschieben"

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:31
msgid ""
"To move a section within the same chapter, you can simply use the drag and "
"drop elements.\n"
"We don't support moving sections within different chapters yet.\n"
"For now, if needed, we suggest the following procedure:\n"
"copy the content of the section on a document;"
msgstr ""

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:31
msgid "delete the section you'd like to move;"
msgstr ""

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:31
msgid "create a new section located at the right place;"
msgstr ""

#: guide/en/wikitolearn-guide-chapter-4.txt:31
msgid "paste the old content and save the page."
msgstr ""
